    "In the case of the newborn, what this also does, we are arguing, is create the basic building block of a moral compass-truth.",
    "Apart from some outliers, it also builds the formative values of a societies.",
    "Thinking purely in terms of socialisation, we can begin to get a sense of the essential difference with large language models.",
    "If left to themselves, large language models would read everything on the internet but on the internet there is no stability, no constancy and no truth; rather there is every possible option and opinion.",
    "An LLM reads everything and then, instead of being restricted to the trustworthy, it calculates probabilities based on all the opinions it finds."
